import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

# 修改代码以显示每个单元格的数值

def plot_correlation_matrix(correlation_matrix):
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 8))

    # 绘制热力图
    cax = ax.imshow(correlation_matrix, interpolation='nearest', cmap='coolwarm', vmin=-1, vmax=1)

    # 添加颜色条
    plt.colorbar(cax, label='Correlation Coefficient')

    # 显示每个单元格的数值
    for i in range(correlation_matrix.shape[0]):
        for j in range(correlation_matrix.shape[1]):
            ax.text(j, i, round(correlation_matrix.iloc[i, j], 2), ha='center', va='center')

    # 设置标题和坐标轴标签
    
    ax.set_title('reilitu---fanjinhao')
    ax.set_xlabel('Feature')
    ax.set_ylabel('Feature')

    plt.show()

from sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression
from sklearn.model_selection import cross_val_score
from sklearn.metrics import f1_score

# 第7步：使用交叉验证训练和评估逻辑回归模型

# 初始化逻辑回归模型
logistic_regression_model = LogisticRegression(max_iter=1000)  # 初始化逻辑回归模型，设置最大迭代次数为1000

# 执行5折交叉验证
# 使用交叉验证评估模型性能，cv=5表示使用5折交叉验证，scoring='f1_macro'表示使用f1宏平均作为评价指标
cross_val_scores = cross_val_score(logistic_regression_model, X_train, y_train, cv=5, scoring='f1_macro')

# 计算f1分数的均值和标准差
mean_f1_score = cross_val_scores.mean()  # 计算f1分数的坝值
std_f1_score = cross_val_scores.std()  # 计算f1分数的标准差

mean_f1_score, std_f1_score

from sklearn.model_selection import GridSearchCV

# 第8步：对逻辑回归模型进行超参数调优的网格搜索

# 定义网格搜索的参数范围
c_range = [0.001, 0.01, 0.1, 1.0]  # 正则化参数C的取值范围
solvers = ['liblinear', 'lbfgs', 'newton-cg', 'sag']  # 优化算法的选择
max_iters = [80, 100, 150, 200, 300]  # 最大迭代次数的取值范围
tuned_parameters = dict(solver=solvers, C=c_range, max_iter=max_iters)  # 定义需要调优的参数组合

# 初始化网格搜索
grid_search = GridSearchCV(logistic_regression_model, tuned_parameters, cv=5, scoring='f1_macro')  # 使用5折交叉验证进行网格搜索，评价指标为f1宏平均

# 执行网格搜索
grid_search.fit(X_train, y_train)

# 获取最佳参数和最佳得分
best_parameters = grid_search.best_params_  # 获取最佳参数组合
best_score = grid_search.best_score_  # 获取最佳得分

best_parameters, best_score

# 第9步：完成模型并进行预测

# 使用最佳参数初始化最终的逻辑回归模型
final_logistic_regression_model = LogisticRegression(**best_parameters)  # 使用网格搜索得到的最佳参数初始化最终的逻辑回归模型

# 在训练数据上训练最终模型

import math
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns

# 绘制每个特征的分布
def plot_distribution(dataset, cols=5, width=20, height=15, hspace=0.2, wspace=0.5):
    plt.style.use('seaborn-whitegrid') 
    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(width,height))
    fig.subplots_adjust(left=None, bottom=None, right=None, top=None, wspace=wspace, hspace=hspace)
    rows = math.ceil(float(dataset.shape[1]) / cols)
    for i, column in enumerate(dataset.columns):
        ax = fig.add_subplot(rows, cols, i + 1)
        ax.set_title(column)  
        if dataset.dtypes[column] == object:
            g = sns.countplot(y=column, data=dataset)
            substrings = [s.get_text()[:18] for s in g.get_yticklabels()]
            g.set(yticklabels=substrings)
            plt.xticks(rotation=25) 
        else:
            g = sns.histplot(data=dataset, x=column, kde=True)  # 使用sns.histplot()代替sns.distplot()
            plt.xticks(rotation=25)

#交叉验证法
from collections import Counter
from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split
from sklearn.model_selection import StratifiedKFold
from sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression
from sklearn.metrics import f1_score
# 创建分层交叉验证的划分器
kf = StratifiedKFold(n_splits=5, shuffle=True, random_state=42)

# 遍历每一折的划分
for train_index, test_index in kf.split(X, y):
    X_train, X_test = X[train_index], X[test_index]
    y_train, y_test = y[train_index], y[test_index]

    # 在当前折的训练集上训练模型，并在测试集上评估模型性能
    lr_model = LogisticRegression()
    lr_model.fit(X_train, y_train)
    y_pred = lr_model.predict(X_test)
    print(f1_score(y_test, y_pred))       
print('Distribution of y_train {}'.format(Counter(y_train)))
print('Distribution of y_test {}'.format(Counter(y_test)))
